      "span_text": "Additionally, as reported in Figure 2B , the fluorescence intensity of PLGA-PEG-RhB-NPs was not greatly affected by the incubation media showing that, once conjugated, the dye abolishes its pH-dependent emission properties [CITATION_1] . "
